{"cells":[{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["Here is the complete, expert-level rewrite of the core system. We are graduating from a \"script\" to a **Production-Grade Agent**.\n","\n","To achieve this, we are introducing three massive upgrades:\n","\n","1. **Pydantic:** This acts as a strict border patrol. If Claude hallucinates a data type or forgets a field, the code throws an error immediately rather than trading on bad data.\n","2. **Anthropic Tool Use:** We force Claude to use a native JSON-schema tool rather than politely asking it to output markdown JSON.\n","3. **SQLite:** We are replacing the fragile `briefs.jsonl` file with a robust, thread-safe database to prevent race conditions when the Slack receiver and Scheduler run at the same time.\n","\n","Before running this, you will need to add Pydantic to your environment:\n","\n","```bash\n","pip install anthropic requests pytz pydantic\n","\n","```\n","\n","Here are the rewritten, expert-level files.\n","\n","---\n","\n","### 1. `models.py` (The Strict Schema)\n","\n","*This replaces the need to manually guess what Claude returns. It mathematically guarantees the shape of your data.*"],"metadata":{"id":"fs4MGASWaZKo"}},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"faeaaeac","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1776815255350,"user_tz":-60,"elapsed":6577,"user":{"displayName":"Syed Mehrab","userId":"10016417158375832621"}},"outputId":"b380ada3-087a-4ace-ec02-295d77cd3132"},"source":["!pip install anthropic requests pytz pydantic"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Collecting anthropic\n","  Downloading anthropic-0.96.0-py3-none-any.whl.metadata (3.1 kB)\n","Requirement already satisfied: requests in /usr/local/lib/python3.12/dist-packages (2.32.4)\n","Requirement already satisfied: pytz in /usr/local/lib/python3.12/dist-packages (2025.2)\n","Requirement already satisfied: pydantic in /usr/local/lib/python3.12/dist-pa